 1<b>."},{"content":"Add all remaining ingredients, including reserved chopped herbs, and cook <b>60 min\/100°C\/\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Mix contents of bowl with spatula, then cook for a further <b>25 min\/100°C\/\/speed 1<b>. Serve hot (see tip)."}],"hintsAndTricks":["This lamb stew is best served with a side of creamy polenta and steamed vegetables."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","1h 45m","4 portions"]}